Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that exposes weg commands as
structured tools for AI assistants like Claude Code.

Subcommands:
  serve     Start the MCP server on stdio
  install   Generate/update .mcp.json configuration

Quick start:
  weg mcp install        # Add weg to .mcp.json
  weg mcp serve          # Start server (used by AI tools)

Usage:
  mcp [command]

Available Commands:
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  help        Help about any command
  install     Generate/update .mcp.json with weg server config
  serve       Start the MCP server on stdio

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for mcp

Use "mcp [command] --help" for more information about a command.
